  <name>Comgen</name>
  <summary>Comment Generator: generate styled comments for your code.</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Comment Generator will let you create a header block that can include elements like an ascii art title, version number, authors and copyright information.</p>
    <p>Currently the following comment styles are available for use:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>// C++</li>
      <li>/* C */</li>
      <li># Bash</li>
      <li>&lt;!-- HTML --&gt;</li>
      <li>; Assembly</li>
      <li>-- MySQL</li>
      <li>--[[ Lua --]]</li>
      <li>' Visual Basic</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
   <provides>
    <binary>com.github.jeremyvaartjes.comgen</binary>
  </provides>
  
